    "body": "Yes, but why not provide a simple API to translate contents in main and render process. Now I should use two library (one for render in node.js and a second for my front-end Angular). I thing it will be a good feature to add to electron because support user language is very important for an \"pro\" app.\n\nOr if not an API, why not explain or give some library in doc ?\n"
